sequenceDiagram
    participant User
    participant CLI as cli/main.py
    participant Pipeline as AnalysisPipeline
    participant Ingest as ingestion/*
    participant Catalog as ReferenceCatalog
    participant Retrieval as retrieval/*
    participant StageA as StageADetector
    participant StageB as StageBReasoner
    participant Revision as PolicyRevisionEngine
    participant Reporting as reporting/*

    User->>CLI: run with --policy-path
    CLI->>Pipeline: execute(policy_path, domain, output_dir)
    Pipeline->>Pipeline: initialize_resources()
    Pipeline->>Ingest: parse document
    Pipeline->>Ingest: chunk text
    Pipeline->>Retrieval: embed policy chunks + store
    Pipeline->>Catalog: load/get subcategories
    Pipeline->>StageA: deterministic assessments
    StageA-->>Pipeline: coverage assessments
    Pipeline->>StageB: reason on unresolved statuses
    StageB-->>Pipeline: gap details
    Pipeline->>Revision: generate revised policy
    Pipeline->>Reporting: generate reports + roadmap + audit log
    Pipeline-->>CLI: AnalysisResult
    CLI-->>User: summary + output paths
